ygData.subject: Farewell party in Kelethin 7/23 11pmCST
ygData.msgSnippet: Hail, friends! I will be soon be leaving the world we call Norrath =( . I would like to thank all of you for a GREAT time. Special thanks to all Black Moon
ygData.messageBody:
Hail, friends! I will be soon be leaving the
world we call Norrath =( . I would like to thank all of
you for a GREAT time. Special thanks to all Black
Moon members, and extra special gratitude to
Greyhound, Torbrashal, Hunnyb, Qalar, Fareb, and my other
close EQ buddies. In case you were wondering why i am
leaving, my funding has been cut. I have a job but i don't
have a credit card, and if i am not mistaken, that is
the only way to pay for your account. Well, keep
having fun and remember me =`) *sniff sniff*<br> -
Gilerrin Galewind, Ranger of the 32nd Rank (Ret)
